title: Hour 3 - LeBron James vs. Kareem Abdul-Jabbar, Marcellus Wiley
itunes:title: Hour 3 - LeBron James vs. Kareem Abdul-Jabbar, Marcellus Wiley
description:
Dan reminds us that Kareem Abdul-Jabbar is actually the G.O.A.T. as LeBron James is on track to surpass his all-time NBA career scoring record later this season. And he talks to former NFL DE Marcellus Wiley about fighting on the field.
